    [media] dib0700_devices: use DVBv5 parameters on set_params()
    
    Instead of using DVBv3 parameters, rely on DVBv5 parameters to
    set the tuner
    
    Signed-off-by: Mauro Carvalho Chehab <mchehab@redhat.com>

